summary: A new dagger model, based on an antique persian damascus steel & walrus ivory dagger.
descriptionHtml:
Hi there! I made this model as practice for my Maya course, but I figured, now that I've made it, I might as well stuff it in Skyrim. So here it is.

The stats are more or less identical to an Elven dagger. It can be found in the Jarl of Riften's bedroom chambers, but watch out; she owns it, so stealing is the only way you'll be getting it. If this is objectionable I may change that later.

The dagger is based on a genuine persian dagger, made of black Damascus steel and walrus ivory.
author: Catflop aka Maryam
